{"tid":1300440,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大灣區加快建設「社會信用體系」 港府澄清絕不會在港實施","createTime":"2019-07-09T11:11:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T18:15:06.000Z","uid":42122,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"1843315c3d58718cf2ff3b550769adbc7894181e","tid":1300440,"uid":42122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:11:38.000Z","msg":"信嗎?<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://today.line.me/HK/pc/article/EPrm52?utm_source=washare\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftoday.line.me%2FHK%2Fpc%2Farticle%2FEPrm52%3Futm_source%3Dwashare&d=xVNj5QJXHW0KkW%2Bw8ZKC7MdEKmWGZzYthIwftZf8Bt0%3D&h=cf648d59\" target=\"_blank\">https://today.line.me/HK/pc/article/EPrm52?utm_source=washare</a><br />\n就有台灣報章和網上平台指內地的「社會信用體系」將會在香港實施，特區政府發言人澄清絕無此事。港府發言人指出，廣東省7月5日印發推進粵港澳大灣區建設三年行動計劃（2018-2020年），其中包括在廣東省內加快「社會信用體系」建設。該計劃只適用於廣東省；特區政府不會在香港施行「社會信用體系」。<br />\n政制及內地事務局局長聶德權下午亦在社交網站Facebook澄清，指該項措施與香港無關，絕對不會在香港實施。<br />\n國務院自2014年公布「社會信用體系建設」計劃，依照民眾的日常行為，如曾否違反金融合約、網上言論詆毀他人等，為個人進行信用評分，以做到「褒揚誠信，懲戒失信」。國家發改委2018年6月聯同多個政府部門發出公告，「適當限制特定嚴重失信人」乘坐飛機和火車。<br />\n行動計劃提到，「加快社會信用體系和市場監管體系建設。研究制定廣東省社會信用條例。探索依法對大灣區內企業聯動實施信用激勵和失信懲戒。建成全省統一的市場監管信息平台」."},{"pid":"d988066d7791ca412697c00a243ff299b53e3765","tid":1300440,"uid":276548,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:12:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.kym-cdn.com/entries/icons/original/000/000/015/oreally.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.kym-cdn.com%2Fentries%2Ficons%2Foriginal%2F000%2F000%2F015%2Foreally.jpg&h=6e514379&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d3f5b61c96e44166b8dcf98e7015e60810834879","tid":1300440,"uid":263058,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:22:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"528dfc705a8cabaafe9f1b17c0c9a242dfd7554c","tid":1300440,"uid":137459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:23:13.000Z","msg":"《一日爭取唔到真普選，我地永遠處於被動》<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1299151\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1299151</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"914ebe7bfee29e1736b142545e6c188cb840d59a","tid":1300440,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:43:39.000Z","msg":"爭取港獨 反了反了"},{"pid":"8e74b992a73f8f719658821509d2f7c75a87af71","tid":1300440,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:45:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G9dYAX6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG9dYAX6.png&h=5f4c67ec&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b0371517673acf47c1bfcb85d33752cada6d7653","tid":1300440,"uid":140949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:47:11.000Z","msg":"唔信，並時刻保持警剔"},{"pid":"b0e2276da011992cafa974b989a46274059f56d8","tid":1300440,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:48:13.000Z","msg":"鄭汝樺2009年：沒有「一地兩檢」不等於沒有高速"},{"pid":"4c395bdda84b1bba59121ba58382e7d1c924cc20","tid":1300440,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:49:01.000Z","msg":"港共重有人信？"},{"pid":"ffee20b4a91ce229fac44e5e5756ac907df9fe42","tid":1300440,"uid":42122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b0371517673acf47c1bfcb85d33752cada6d7653","tid":1300440,"uid":140949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:47:11.000Z","msg":"唔信，並時刻保持警剔"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T18:15:06.000Z","msg":"早排先講以後只有大灣區無香港"}]}